# Welcome message (Command /start)
info-start-text =
    🤖 Hello! My name is Nexus Shell | AI Agent

    You have connected to a universal shell for working with leading language models. Gemini, GPT, and Claude are now available in one interface within your Telegram.

    To get started, follow three simple steps:

    1️⃣ 🔑 Connect your API key
    Use the /setup command to add your key for the desired model. I support direct integration, ensuring speed and privacy.

    2️⃣ 🧠 Set your System Prompt
    Define the context, role, or behavior rules for your agent. This allows the bot to become an assistant, analyst, or developer.

    3️⃣ 🚀 Start working
    Send regular prompts and your custom agent will instantly get to work on your tasks.

    ---
    Use /help to find out how to get an API key.

